в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ expressivity                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - The current design uses only RY rotations and CZ entanglers, which is relatively     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ restrictive                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - No parametrized two-qubit gates are present, limiting the circuit's ability to learn в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ complex correlations                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - The feature map uses only RX, and the ansatz uses only RYвҖ”adding RZ rotations can    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ provide additional degrees of freedom                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 3. **Proposed improvements**:                                                             в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - **Add RZ rotations** on select qubits (corners and edges) to increase expressivity   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ without excessive parameter growth                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - **Reintroduce parametrized controlled rotations** but use CRZ (instead of CRX) on    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ center-connected edges, as CRZ provides better phase-space coverage for tic-tac-toe       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ classification                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - **Maintain parameter efficiency** by using selective parameter sharing: corners      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ share one RZ parameter, edges share another                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - This adds ~6-8 new parameters while maintaining circuit depth efficiency             в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 4. **Rationale**:                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - RZ gates complement RY gates and the RX feature map, providing full SU(2) coverage   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ per qubit                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - CRZ entanglers on center connections (1-8, 3-8, 5-8, 7-8) are geometrically          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ meaningful for tic-tac-toe structure                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - Selective sharing keeps parameter count low while allowing the circuit to learn      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ class-specific rotations                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ    - This design balances expressivity (to improve accuracy) with parameter efficiency    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ (to maintain generalization)                                                              в”Ӯ
