в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ decrease N_PARAMS_PER_BLOCK from 7 to 4 (3 RY params + 1 shared CRX param). This should   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ improve generalization and training efficiency (fewer trainable parameters) while         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ retaining the data-reuploading structure and adjacency constraints. The block remains     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ expressive due to multiple center-edge entanglers using the same tunable strength, and    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ symmetry is encouraged across the four connections.                                       в”Ӯ
